      <h3 class="c-entry-box-base__headline"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/16/21223320/gopro-fires-20-percent-of-business-200-employees-coronavirus-ceo-pay-cut-drone-recovery">GoPro cuts 20 percent of workforce after being hit hard by pandemic</a></h3>
    

  
    
      
        <p class="c-entry-box-base__dek p-dek c-entry-box-base__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">A year after it started to recover from its drone disaster</p>
      
    

    

  
    
      
      
        
